        <h1>Is Your Pet Bird A Boy or Girl? Find Out Here!</h1>
        <div class="post-info"><span class="theauthor">By <span itemprop="author">My VGC</span></span> <span class="thetime">On <span itemprop="datePublished">March 26, 2014</span></span> <span class="thecomment"><span itemprop="interactionCount">5 Comments</span></span></div>
